-- FTC approves GE purchase of Avio's aviation business
-- 
-- Fri Jul 19, 2013 5:48pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/07/19/us-aviation-ge-antitrust-idUSBRE96I16Q20130719

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - General Electric ( GE.N ) won U.S. antitrust approval for its $4.3 billion bid for Italian plane components maker Avio, the Federal Trade Commission said on Friday. 
 General Electric won EU clearance for the transaction on Tuesday, after agreeing to protect strategic information related to the Eurofighter project. (Reporting by  Diane Bartz )